{"tid":290403,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"蚊型睡房裝修，巴絲請出招","createTime":"2017-06-19T17:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T15:37:41.000Z","uid":7786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e68779996db818143990dd11bf4820d5245d3a","tid":290403,"uid":7786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:50:54.000Z","msg":"個蚊型睡房得 1.8米x2米左右，計埋個陀衰家窗台就約2mx2m <br />\n<br />\n睇設計公司啲行貨睇到悶，想睇下有創意既連登巴打有冇咩idea? <br />\n<br />\n暫時小弟只諗過<br />\n1. 升高地台<br />\n2. 整拉床<br />\n就好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/015012_01a5805f954b4725a358aec905b4f85b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F015012_01a5805f954b4725a358aec905b4f85b.jpg&h=00452a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係想有基本床，書枱同衣櫃... <br />\n<br />\n點解喺香港生活咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴打請出招！"},{"pid":"d706cec96c749736b6b7e117abd63649ca61adf3","tid":290403,"uid":14479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:56:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2e5a4567b47c05a6ce7d04a2d86716c951d12c1b","tid":290403,"uid":18564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:56:18.000Z","msg":"點解唔整碌架床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 滿足哂你三個要求"},{"pid":"92cd62b811dd202c07a2e32cceec0bef2de3cb1d","tid":290403,"uid":7786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔整碌架床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 滿足哂你三個要求</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有諗過，而家用緊碌架床。但起身好易撞到燈。同埋想睇下有冇啲有創意既做法：）"},{"pid":"960bdc942c588d018b208711534978f98af010d4","tid":290403,"uid":18564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"拉床個設計<br />\n你間房個size整既話<br />\n開左張床出黎就會開唔到門<br />\n(定你間房係整趟門?)"},{"pid":"a2731638e4f0b45